snippet.title: WATERMELON JELLY | Fresh Colorful Fruit Jelly Recipe Making in Village | Agar Agar Jelly Cooking
snippet.description: This video showcases the making of a healthy, fresh, and natural fruit jelly using a variety of colorful fruits, sugar, and agar agar. The combination of fresh fruits adds natural sweetness and a delightful texture, while agar agar helps create a perfect jelly consistency. This refreshing dessert is not only visually stunning but also a light and healthy treat, made using simple ingredients without any artificial additives. Watch the entire process as we prepare, set, and slice this beautiful jelly, bringing out the flavors of nature’s best ingredients in a traditional village-style preparation.

snippet.title: NZ vs PAK 2nd T20I - Cricket Highlights | Pakistan Tour Of New Zealand 2025 | Prime Video India
snippet.description:
New Zealand takes a 2-0 lead in the Pakistan Tour of New Zealand! 🏏🔥 Tim Seifert's blistering 45 off 22 balls, including four sixes in a single over from Shaheen Afridi, propelled the Kiwis to a dominant win. Pakistan posted 135/9, but New Zealand chased down 137/5 with ease. Stay tuned for all the action and more cricket highlights!

Watch the entire match here: https://bit.ly/NewZealandvsPakistan2ndT20IOnPrime

snippet.title: NZ Vs PAK 1st T20i | Cricket Highlights | Pakistan Tour Of New Zealand | 16th March 2025
snippet.description:
In the 1st T20I, New Zealand won the toss and decided to bowl first and invited Pakistan to bat first. Pakistan was cheaply dismissed on the score of 91 runs in 18.4 overs. New Zealand chased down the target in just 10.1 overs and won the match by 9 wickets.

snippet.title: Aurangzeb की कब्र के पास के दुकानदारों ने कब्र की राजनीती पर क्या कहा? Ground Report|SN
snippet.description:
#AurangzebTomb #AurangzebControversy #AurangzebNews
Aurangzeb Tomb Controversy news : महाराष्ट्र में औरंगज़ेब की कब्र को हटाने की मांग हिन्दू संगठनों की तरफ से जोरो में की जा रही है. VHP और बजरंग दल ने सरकार को अल्टीमेटम दिया है. इसी बीच हमारी टीम छत्रपति संभाजी नगर पहुंची और यहां पहुंचकर हमने औरंगज़ेब की कब्र के आस पास के दुकान वालो से बात की और उनसे जानने की कोशिश की की आखिर वो क्या सोचते है औरंगज़ेब की कब्र पर चल रही इस राजनीती को लेकर.



--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

snippet.title: Sunita Williams Smiles And Waves At The Camera After Her Safe Return To Earth
snippet.description:
NASA astronauts Sunita Williams and Butch Wilmore have successfully returned to Earth after 9 months in in space. The SpaceX capsule 'Freedom' splashed down at 3:28 a.m., concluding a mission extended due to technical issues. The landing, involving complex de-orbiting and seven crucial phases, proceeded as planned. The astronauts will undergo medical examinations upon return.

snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Aas Paas Episode 17 - [Eng Sub] - Laiba Khan - Ali Ansari - 18th March 2025 - HAR PAL GEO

Aas Paas is a story of love, sacrifice, and the struggles within the relationships we often take for granted.
Arshia, a strong-willed young woman, is determined to reunite her broken family after her father abandons them. Meanwhile, Dr. Saham, a dedicated professional carrying his own burdens,
crosses paths with her.
Bound by their selflessness, they embark on a journey where their devotion to family is tested, and their own happiness is put on the line.
Will Arshia succeed in bringing her family back together? What challenges await Dr. Saham and Arshia? Could love blossom between them?

7th Sky Entertainment Presentation
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Director: Muhammad Iftikhar Iffi
Writer: Samra Bukhari

Cast:
Ali Ansari as Dr. Saham
Laiba Khan as Arshia/Arshi

Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Aas Paas Episode 17 - [Eng Sub] - Laiba Khan - Ali Ansari - 18th March 2025 - HAR PAL GEO

Aas Paas is a story of love, sacrifice, and the struggles within the relationships we often take for granted.
Arshia, a strong-willed young woman, is determined to reunite her broken family after her father abandons them. Meanwhile, Dr. Saham, a dedicated professional carrying his own burdens,
crosses paths with her.
Bound by their selflessness, they embark on a journey where their devotion to family is tested, and their own happiness is put on the line.
Will Arshia succeed in bringing her family back together? What challenges await Dr. Saham and Arshia? Could love blossom between them?

7th Sky Entertainment Presentation
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Director: Muhammad Iftikhar Iffi
Writer: Samra Bukhari

Cast:
Ali Ansari as Dr. Saham
Laiba Khan as Arshia/Arshi
Samina Ahmed as Aneeqa Begum
Saba Faisal as Seemab
Saife Hasan as Kamal
Sahiba Afzal as Kashifa
Afzal Khan (Jan Rambo) as Ausaf 
Namra Shahid as Shagoofa 
Fahima Awan as Aneela
Faisal Naqvi as Musheer
Alina Chaudhry as Aneela's Mother-in-law 
Nain Sukh as Anooshia/Anooshi
Ahsan Afzal Khan as Ammad
Ahmed Usman as Shehroze

snippet.title: Sunita Williams Return to Earth Process Explained | సునీతా విలియమ్స్ భూమ్మీదకు వచ్చే విధానం ఇలా| ABP
snippet.description:
#sunitawilliams #Nasa #SpaceX #Crew9 #Interantionalspacestation #ABPDesam #telugunews

   నాసా ఆస్ట్రానాట్, మన భారతీయ మూలాలున్న మహిళ సునీతా విలియమ్స్ తొమ్మిదినెలలుగా అంతరిక్షంలోనే చిక్కుకుపోయారని మనకందరికీ తెలుసు కదా. ఎట్టకేలకు ఆమె భూమ్మీదకు దిగే ప్రక్రియ ఈ మంగళవారం ప్రారంభం అవుతోంది. క్రూ10 అంతర్జాతీయ అంతరిక్ష కేంద్రానికి వేసుకొచ్చిన ఎలన్ మస్క్ స్పేస్ ఎక్స్ వాళ్ల డ్రాగన్ క్యాప్సూల్ లోనే క్రూ 9 భూమ్మీదకు దిగుతోంది. క్రూ 9లో మొత్తం నలుగురు ఉంటారు. సునీతా విలియమ్స్ తో పాటు స్పేస్ లో చిక్కుకుపోయిన బుచ్ విల్ మోర్...ఇంకా నిక్ హేగ్, రష్యా కాస్మోనాట్ అలెగ్జాండర్ గోర్బునోవ్ కూడా ఉంటారు. అయితే వీళ్లు భూమ్మీదకు దిగే ప్రోసెస్ దశల వారీగా జరుగుతుంది. అవేంటో డీటైల్డ్ గా చెప్పుకుందాం.


Sunita Williams Return to Earth Process Explained | సునీతా విలియమ్స్ భూమ్మీదకు వచ్చే విధానం ఇలా| ABP

   నాసా ఆస్ట్రానాట్, మన భారతీయ మూలాలున్న మహిళ సునీతా విలియమ్స్ తొమ్మిదినెలలుగా అంతరిక్షంలోనే చిక్కుకుపోయారని మనకందరికీ తెలుసు కదా. ఎట్టకేలకు ఆమె భూమ్మీదకు దిగే ప్రక్రియ ఈ మంగళవారం ప్రారంభం అవుతోంది. క్రూ10 అంతర్జాతీయ అంతరిక్ష కేంద్రానికి వేసుకొచ్చిన ఎలన్ మస్క్ స్పేస్ ఎక్స్ వాళ్ల డ్రాగన్ క్యాప్సూల్ లోనే క్రూ 9 భూమ్మీదకు దిగుతోంది. క్రూ 9లో మొత్తం నలుగురు ఉంటారు. సునీతా విలియమ్స్ తో పాటు స్పేస్ లో చిక్కుకుపోయిన బుచ్ విల్ మోర్...ఇంకా నిక్ హేగ్, రష్యా కాస్మోనాట్ అలెగ్జాండర్ గోర్బునోవ్ కూడా ఉంటారు. అయితే వీళ్లు భూమ్మీదకు దిగే ప్రోసెస్ దశల వారీగా జరుగుతుంది. అవేంటో డీటైల్డ్ గా చెప్పుకుందాం.


Sunita Williams Return to Earth Process Explained | సునీతా విలియమ్స్ భూమ్మీదకు వచ్చే విధానం ఇలా| ABP

Episode 4348: Taarak Ke Liye Mithai
--------------------------------------------------------
Popatlal creates an uproar in the society over earth sacks littering the compound. Later, Bhide contacts Bhoothnath to reprimand him for the mess.

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: The Lavari Show EP 38 | ft. Paresh Ganatra | Meme Legend | The Comedy Factory
snippet.description:
Special Guest - Paresh Ganatra
Paresh Ganatra is an Indian actor and comedian known for his work in television, films, and theater. He began his acting career during his college days by performing in theater. Paresh made his film debut in 1999 with "Mann" and gained prominence for his role as Praveen Thakkar in the TV series "Baa Bahoo Aur Baby" (2005–2010). He is also known for his performances in films like "No Entry" (2005), "Welcome" (2007), and "Rowdy Rathore" (2012).

Apart from movies and daily soaps, Paresh Ganatra is also well-known for his particiaption in the comedy reality TV shows like “Comedy Circus 3 Ka Tadka,” “Comedy Circus Mahasangram,” and “Comedy Circus Ke SuperStars.” He has also played different characters in “Comedy Nights with Kapil” (2013–2016), and “The Kapil Sharma Show” (2016–2017).

Artists - 
Manan Desai, Om Bhatt, Deep Vaidya & Chirayu Mistry

snippet.title: NASA’s SpaceX Crew-9 Undocking
snippet.description:
Watch as the four members of NASA's SpaceX Crew-9 mission—NASA astronauts Nick Hague, Suni Williams, Butch Wilmore, and cosmonaut Aleksandr Gorbunov—undock from the International Space Station and begin their journey home to Earth.

Crew-9's SpaceX Dragon spacecraft is scheduled to undock from the International Space Station at 1:05 a.m. EST (0505 UTC). After undocking from the station, Crew-9 is scheduled to splash down off the coast of Florida at 5:57 p.m. EDT (2157 UTC), ending their multi-month mission in low Earth orbit.

See the full schedule for Crew-9's return to Earth: https://go.nasa.gov/4iWeg8N
Learn more about Crew-9's scientific mission: https://go.nasa.gov/4bWdt5u
Follow the latest Crew-9 mission updates: https://www.nasa.gov/blogs/commercialcrew/

Credit: NASA

snippet.title: Tigmanshu Dhulia's The Promise – A Must-Watch | Royal Stag Barrel Select Shorts
snippet.description:
In Tigmanshu Dhulia's poignant masterpiece ‘The Promise,’ Royal Stag Barrel Select Shorts delivers a soul-stirring tale that exemplifies the best of select storytelling.

When Delhi newcomer Chitra (played by Priyamani) crosses paths with George (played by Jim Sarbh), a bartender from Greater Kailash 1, an unexpected connection blossoms. As they share fragments of their pasts, their bond deepens, transcending fleeting moments into something profound and unspoken. But fate has other plans. George receives his long-awaited M.Tech acceptance letter, and in a moment of quiet heartbreak, Chitra chooses to step away, ensuring he pursues his dreams. Their farewell is sealed with a promise—to meet again at the same place, 20 years later.

Two decades pass. George returns to the same place, carrying the weight of the past and the anticipation of what lies ahead. But what he discovers changes everything. ‘The Promise’ is not just a story—it’s an emotional journey that lingers, reminding us that some bonds are meant to withstand the test of time.

‘The Promise’ stands as a testament to select filmmaking—where nuanced emotions, evolved storytelling techniques, and sophisticated narrative choices elevate cinema beyond mainstream conventions.

#BarrelSelect #RoyalStagBarrelSelectLargeShortFilms #RoyalStagBarrelSelectShorts #theselectones  #ForTheSelectOnes #JimSarbh #Priyamani #TigmanshuDhulia #shortfilm

snippet.title: Sunita Williams Countdown to Earth 🔥 🚀 | Madan Gowri | Tamil | MG Squad 🖖🏻
snippet.description:
In this video, Madan Gowri explains the highly anticipated return of astronaut Sunita Williams after spending months in space aboard the International Space Station (ISS). After her 9-month mission, she is set to return to Earth safely soon, facing a re-entry through Earth’s atmosphere. This process exposes astronauts to extreme G-forces, pushing their bodies to the limit. After months in microgravity, astronauts experience muscle loss, weakened bones, and balance issues, making the transition back to Earth’s gravity a major challenge. The final stage of her return? A high-speed descent and a dramatic splashdown in the ocean. Even after landing, she’ll need time to recover from space travel. But how does NASA prepare astronauts for this? What changes will she face during re-entry and splashdown? Will it be a smooth landing or a bumpy ride back home? This return will test her mental and physical endurance like never before.  With space exploration expanding towards the Moon, Mars, and beyond, missions like these are crucial for the future of human spaceflight. Could India play a role in future interplanetary missions? Stay tuned to find out!

snippet.title: ‌UP Mosque Covered in Tarpuline : হোলি উৎসবে যোগীরাজ্যে মসজিদ ঢাকল ত্রিপলে এ কোন ভারত! N18P
snippet.description:
‌UP Mosque Covered in Tarpuline : মার্চেই শুরু হয়েছে পবিত্র রমজান মাস। একে রমজান তায় আবার শুক্রবার। সেদিনই আবার দোলপূর্ণিমা। কীভাবে সামাল দেবে? 
চিন্তায় ছিল ‌যোগী সরকার। তবে সমাধান মিলেছে। ইতিমধ্যেই প্রয়াগরাজে ১৪ তারিখ। রমজানের নামাজ পরার সময়ে। দুপুর ২টোর পর পিছিয়ে নিয়ে ‌যাওয়া হয়েছে। এছাড়াও দোলের রঙের থেকে বাঁচাতে।  উত্তরপ্রদেশের ৪টি জেলার প্রায় ১৮৯ টি মসজিদকে ঢাকা হয়েছে ত্রিপলে । 

#upmosquecoveredintarpuline #yogiadityanath #sambhal #holi2025 #dol2025 #news18originals #banglanews

snippet.title: Phone Ma Status Gum Na Rakhe | Reshma Thakor, Dinesh Thakor | New Gujarati Sad Song 2025
snippet.description:
સાંભળો રેશમા ઠાકોર અને દિનેશ ઠાકોર નું નવું હૃદયસ્પર્શી ઈમોશનલ ગીત "ફોન મા સ્ટેટસ ગમ ના રાખે" માત્ર @SaregamaGujarati  પર.

Credits:
Title : Phone Ma Status Gum Na Rakhe
Singer : Reshma Thakor, Dinesh Thakor
Producer: Red Velvet Cinema
Artist : Dinesh Thakor, Vidhi Shah, Bharat Chaudhary
Director, Concept & Edit : Rakesh Kumar (RK Sir)
Music: Shashi Kapdiya
Lyrics: R.K.Thakor
Creative Producer: Dhyey Films & Team
Technical Support: Jenish Talaviya
D.O.P :  Prakash Patel
Drone : Veersinh
Co Artist : Hasmukh Thakor, Arvind Manekpura, Smita, Jakir Pathan
Makeup & Hair : Smita Goswami
Production : Veersinh
SP. Thanks : Kamlesh Raval, D.A. Vaghela, Sadulkhan Pathan
Light : Kalpesh Jadav
Poster Design : Pradip Karbatiya

Lyrics:
હે અલ્યા એ ફોન મો સ્ટેટસ ગમના રાખે
રાખે દર્દીલા ગીત તારે શું દુઃખ પડ્યુ લ્યા
હે અલી એ વાત કેતા મારી જીભ ના ઉપડે
ઉપડે ના મારો પગ  ખોટી તારી વાત મળી સે
હો વાત કરી હોય એ મોણસને લાવો મારી હોમે
ઘરની માતા એ દીવા ઉપડાવું હેડો મારા ગોમે
હે અલી એ તુ કેતો હું પ્રૂફ બતાવુ
બતાવું ફોટા ફોનમાં તેતો સેલ્ફી પાડ્યા
હો મેતો ગોડા ગોમ સોડ્યું તારા વિશ્વાસે
તને નઇ ભુલું મારા છેલ્લા આ શ્વાસે
હો હૂતો બેઠો હતો ખાલી તારા રે ભરોસે
ઘરે શું જવાબ આલુ મારે હવે મરો સે
હો ઘરનો તારો ઉંબરો કદી હુનો નઇ પડવાદુ
તૂ કેતો હું ગોમનિ બારે જવાનું રેવાદુ
હે અલી હે રોજ ઓટા તુ ગોમમાં મારે
મારે તુ મેઠા ટોન ખોટું મને ગમતું નથી
હો  જીવું સુ તને જોઈને જિવવાદે
હગી ઓખે ભલે જોયુ પડતુ એ રેવાદે
હો તારાથી કંટાળ્યો હવે મને તુ મરવાદે
ગોમમા લાગે બધા વસે નઇ જીવવાદે
હો હગઇ કરી એ મુરતિયો ફરવા મને લઈ જ્યો
ફોટા ફર્યા વોટસઅપ માં પસ્તાવો મને થઈ જ્યો
હે અલી એ તારે મારે હવે મેળ નઇ પડે
નઇ પડે હવે રાત મોઢું તારું ભાળવુ નથી

હે અલી હે રોજ ઓટા તુ ગોમમાં મારે
મારે તુ મેઠા ટોન ખોટું મને ગમતું નથી
હો  જીવું સુ તને જોઈને જિવવાદે
હગી ઓખે ભલે જોયુ પડતુ એ રેવાદે
હો તારાથી કંટાળ્યો હવે મને તુ મરવાદે
ગોમમા લાગે બધા વસે નઇ જીવવાદે
હો હગઇ કરી એ મુરતિયો ફરવા મને લઈ જ્યો
ફોટા ફર્યા વોટસઅપ માં પસ્તાવો મને થઈ જ્યો
હે અલી એ તારે મારે હવે મેળ નઇ પડે

Filmymoji Middle Class Madhu releases the continuation episode of Burra Katha Graduates. In this new episode our natal Gutala gang fathers receives a strict warning from the principal of gnaanandham about their kids behaviour. Aas Paas Episode 15 - [Eng Sub] - Laiba Khan - Ali Ansari - 16th March 2025 - HAR PAL GEO

Aas Paas is a story of love, sacrifice, and the struggles within the relationships we often take for granted.
Arshia, a strong-willed young woman, is determined to reunite her broken family after her father abandons them. Meanwhile, Dr. Saham, a dedicated professional carrying his own burdens,
crosses paths with her.
Bound by their selflessness, they embark on a journey where their devotion to family is tested, and their own happiness is put on the line.
Will Arshia succeed in bringing her family back together? What challenges await Dr. Saham and Arshia? Could love blossom between them?

pa.title: ਕੀ ਤੁਸੀਂ ਇੱਕ ਸਵੈ-ਚਲਾਉਣ ਵਾਲੀ ਕਾਰ ਨੂੰ ਠੱਗ ਸਕਦੇ ਹੋ?
pa.description:
ਲੇਜ਼ਰਾਂ ਦੀ ਤਾਕਤ ਨੂੰ ਕਦੇ ਘਟਾ ਨਾ ਅੰਕਣਾ! ਇਕ ਇੰਜੀਨੀਅਰ ਵਾਂਗ ਸੋਚਣਾ ਸਿੱਖਣ ਵਿੱਚ ਮਜ਼ਾ ਆਉ ਜਾਂਦਾ ਹੈ ਅਤੇ http://crunchlabs.com/Lidar 'ਤੇ 2 ਮੁਫਤ ਬਾਕਸ ਪ੍ਰਾਪਤ ਕਰੋ।

ਆਪਣਾ ਕ੍ਰੰਚ ਲੈਬਸ ਬਾਕਸ ਅੱਜ ਹੀ ਪ੍ਰਾਪਤ ਕਰੋ:
ਬੱਚਿਆਂ ਲਈ ਬਿਲਡ ਬਾਕਸ ਇੱਥੇ ਕਲਿੱਕ ਕਰੋ: http://crunchlabs.com/Lidar
ਟੀਨ ਏਜਰ ਅਤੇ ਵੱਡਿਆਂ ਲਈ ਹੈਕ ਪੈਕ ਇੱਥੇ ਕਲਿੱਕ ਕਰੋ: http://crunchlabs.com/LidarHP

ਸਾਡੇ ਨਾਲ ਆਪਣੀ ਲਾਈਡਰ ਕਾਰ ਟੈਸਟ ਕਰਨ ਲਈ ਲੂਮਿਨਾਰ ਦਾ ਧੰਨਵਾਦ: https://www.luminartech.com/

ਰਾਕ ਰੋਬੋਟਿਕ ਦੇ ਹੈਰਿਸਨ @IndianaDrones ਦਾ ਧੰਨਵਾਦ ਜੋ ਆਪਣੇ ਬਹੁਤ ਕੂਲ ਲਾਈਡਰ ਨਾਲ ਮਦਦ ਕਰਨ ਲਈ ਸਾਨੂੰ ਮਿਲੇ। ਇਸ ਪ੍ਰਜੈਕਟ ਤੋਂ ਸਕੈਨਸ ਅਤੇ ਕ੍ਰੰਚ ਲੈਬਸ ਦਾ 3D ਟੂਰ ਦੇਖਣ ਲਈ ਤੁਸੀਂ https://www.rockrobotic.com/ 'ਤੇ ਜਾ ਸਕਦੇ ਹੋ।

ਵੀਡੀਓ ਵਿੱਚ ਕੁਝ ਸੰਗੀਤ ਪ੍ਰਦਾਨ ਕਰਨ ਲਈ ਇਨ੍ਹਾਂ ਲੋਕਾਂ ਦਾ ਧੰਨਵਾਦ:
ਪੌਂਡਰ - @Pondermusic

snippet.title: NEW! Ep 4347 - Jethalal ne Diya Taarak Ko Surprise Gift?! | Taarak Mehta ka Ooltah Chashmah
snippet.description:
Tapu ki Shadi | Gokuldham Society | Sonu ki shadi

Click here to Subscribe to Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Official Channel: https://www.youtube.com/taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah?sub_confirmation=1 

Click here to watch NEW Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzSxhJ6UCi6tgujD-FsAy0sw

Click here to watch your favourite videos from Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.
